TODO a migrer avant de passer à 18:
A lire qui peut aider (l'autre lien est mort): https://v17.material.angular.dev/guide/mdc-migration
autre resource utile: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/75296947/what-to-do-with-legacy-after-angular-v15-update


    Cannot update to Angular Material v17 because the project is using the legacy Material components
    that have been deleted. While Angular Material v16 is compatible with Angular v17, it is recommended
    to switch away from the legacy components as soon as possible because they no longer receive bug fixes,
    accessibility improvements and new features.

    Read more about migrating away from legacy components: https://material.angular.io/guide/mdc-migration

    Files in the project using legacy Material components:
     - /src/app/app.component.ts
     - /src/app/app.module.ts
     - /src/app/components/appstate/uploaddialog/uploaddialog.component.ts
     - /src/app/components/configuration/configdialog/configdialog.component.ts
     - /src/app/components/genericpurposedialog/genericpurposedialog.component.ts
     - /src/app/components/movies/movie/movie.component.ts
